OL,3,CWhat is the two-child benefit cap and
OL,4,Chow many kids does it impact?
OL,6,FApril will see the end of the two-
OL,7,Fchild benefit cap, which limits
OL,8,Funiversal credit and tax credit claims
OL,9,Fto two children in most households,
OL,10,FReeves said.
OL,12,FLifting the cap is expected to cost
OL,13,Fbillions. The chancellor said her
OL,14,Fdecision was "fully costed and fully
OL,15,Ffunded" as through a crackdown on tax
OL,16,Favoidance and gambling tax changes.
