OL,3,CWhat is the two-child benefit cap and
OL,4,Chow many kids does it impact?
OL,6,FWhat is the two-child benefit cap?
OL,8,FThe two-child benefit cap was
OL,9,Fintroduced in 2015 by the
OL,10,FConservatives and came into effect in
OL,11,F2017.
OL,13,FIt restricts the child tax credit and
OL,14,Funiversal credit (UC) to the first two
OL,15,Fchildren in most households, and only
OL,16,Fapplies to children born after 6 April
OL,17,F2017.
