OL,3,CWhat is the two-child benefit cap and
OL,4,Chow many kids does it impact?
OL,6,FThe Conservatives introduced the
OL,7,Fpolicy in an effort to incentivise out-
OL,8,Fof-work parents into employment,
OL,9,Farguing people on benefits "should
OL,10,Fface the same financial choices about
OL,11,Fhaving children as those supporting
OL,12,Fthemselves solely through work".
OL,14,FHow many children does it affect?
OL,16,FOver 1.5 million children are
OL,17,Fcurrently living in households
OL,18,Faffected by the two-child limit, which
OL,19,Faffects one in nine children in the UK.
