OL,3,CWhat is the two-child benefit cap and
OL,4,Chow many kids does it impact?
OL,6,FHas the government's position changed?
OL,8,FThe scrapping of the policy is a
OL,9,Fsignificant shift from its position a
OL,10,Fyear ago.
OL,12,FAxing the cap was not in the Labour
OL,13,Fmanifesto; instead, Starmer promised
OL,14,Fto "develop an ambitious strategy to
OL,15,Freduce child poverty".
OL,17,FJust after Labour won the election
OL,18,Flast July, Starmer suspended seven MPs
OL,19,Fwho voted in favour of an SNP motion
OL,20,Fcalling for the cap to be abolished.
